
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome Page</title>
    <style>
       

        .welcome-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .welcome-header {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .welcome-content {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .welcome-button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .welcome-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .welcome-image {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #999;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="welcome-container">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Welcome Image" class="welcome-image">
        <div class="welcome-header">Bem-vindo à nossa Página Admin!</div>
        <div class="welcome-content">
            Página de teste de Roles , nesta pagina conseguimos identificar Membros , Guests e Admins
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
